headline: Marathon Petroleum vs Phillips 66: Which Refining Giant Wins as Energy Sector Dominates 2026?
summary: Marathon Petroleum (NYSE: MPC) and Phillips 66 (NYSE: PSX) just reported fourth-quarter earnings that underscore why refiners are riding the energy sector’s extraordinary run.
